decoNote.desc:
A miniature of the art theme  with four episodes, showing:
                                   first, the two brothers sitting and writing next to each other;
                                   second, the demons hanging the soul of one of the scribes;
                                   third,  pulling down the scribe's
                                   soul from the demons; fourth, the scribe sitting again and
                                   resuming his writing with his brother.
